# Drop any .ppn wake word model files here — ALL of them are loaded simultaneously.
#
# Recommended: generate both variants at https://console.picovoice.ai/ppn
# (select your OS platform for each, one keyword per model)
#
#   hey-charles.ppn   ← "Hey Charles"
#   charles.ppn       ← "Charles"
#
# Both files will be auto-discovered and loaded together so either phrase
# triggers a voice interaction.  You can add as many variants as you like.
#
# Piper voice model files also live here (auto-downloaded on first run):
#   en_US-lessac-medium.onnx
#   en_US-lessac-medium.onnx.json
#
# Source: https://huggingface.co/rhasspy/piper-voices
